bfdc2210-0675-4b29-be94-c1b91d89b1c5.2543a4f5-02d4-4c38-bfa5-e8a6887ec2ce.description=
 Flow that wraps RAS script export-policy-get-iter.pl which wraps Ontap API method export-policy-get-iter.

Purpose\: Get a group of Export policy configurations.

Inputs\:
clusterName\: mandatory (specifies endpoint to run API against).
vServerName\: optional (Vserver name)
policyName\: optional (Export policy name)
policyId\: optional (Export policy id.)

Optional inputs restrict the search, if none are given, all export polcites in the cluster are returned.

Eg output (eg inputs were clusterName and vServerName)\:


        
                
                        5501853106178
                        S223000SL7NAS01_root
                        S223000SL7NAS01
                
                
                        5501853106179
                        S223000SL7VOL01
                        S223000SL7NAS01
                
                
                        5501853106177
                        default
                        S223000SL7NAS01
                
        
        3

bfdc2210-0675-4b29-be94-c1b91d89b1c5.description=
Synopsis

    This flow sets the configuration for the volume auto size.
    setSusVolAutoSizeConfig performs the following steps\:
      1. Shrink the threshold percent.
      2. Set the minimum size percentage.
      3. Retrieve the vServer based on the vServerName using the HPOO flow getVserver.
      4. Check that the vServer exists.
      5. Retrieve the volume details.
      6. Check that the volume exists.
      7. Calculate the increment size percent.
      8. Calculate the minimum size percent.
      9. Calculate the maximum size percent.
    10. Calculate the increment size percent.
    11. Calculate the minimum size.
    12. Calculate the maximum size.
    13. Set the volume's configuration automatic sizing.
    14. Pass the information back to the requesting entity.

Inputs

    clusterName - The IP or host name of the NetApp cluster (required).
      Valid values\: Dot-decimal notation IPv4 address or RFC 1123 compliant host name.
      Default value\: None.

    vServerName - The name of the vServer used in the flow (required).
